## Building NEO

### Prerequisites

- Rust 1.70+
- For WASM: `wasm-pack`

### Binary (Standalone)

```bash
cargo build --release --bin neo
./target/release/neo
```

### Library (Backend Integration)

```bash
cargo build --release -p neo-lib
```

### WebAssembly (Frontend)

```bash
wasm-pack build neo-wasm --target web
```

